Package: ivx
Type: Package
Title: Robust Econometric Inference
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
            person("Kostas", "Vasilopoulos", , email = "k.vasilopoulo@gmail.com", c("cre", "aut")),
            person("Eftymios", "Pavlidis", email = "e.pavlidis@lancaster.ac.uk", role = "aut"))
Description: 
    Conducting inference on the regression coefficient with a highly persistent regressor,
    using the the IVX approach for univariate (Magdalinos and Phillips, 2009b) and multivariate
    (Kostakis Magdalinos and Stamatogiannis, 2015) regression. Testing can be used for long-horizon 
    predictability as well.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.1)
Imports:
  Rcpp (>= 0.12.18),
  magrittr
Suggests: 
    covr,
    spelling,
    testthat
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/kvasilopoulos/ivx
BugReports: https://github.com/kvasilopoulos/ivx/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Language: en-US
